data.title: June 1 - Courtney Patton | Jason Eady | with Scott Kirby
data.meta_description:
Join us for a fantastic show by Courtney Patton - followed by Jason Eady. Scott Kirby will open the night of entertainment!
Click 'Read More' for further details and information!
data.text:
Date: Thursday, June 1, 2023

Time: Scott Kirby will open at 7:00 PM | Courtney Patton will take the stage at 7:45 PM | Jason Eady will perform at 8:45 PM

Location: Birdsong Amphitheater | 644 S. Graham - Stephenville, Texas 76401

FREE ADMISSION

To ensure you fully enjoy your evening with us please bring your own chairs, pillows or blankets for seating, snacks, and drinks (BYOB - alcohol is allowed) . Bug spray is recommended!

Please respect our park along with all of the attendees and facilities.

Thank you to our sponsors!

Texstar Kubota, Triple Crown Ford, First Financial Bank, and the City of Stephenville
